c: 11
v: 35
t: "Do they (the idolaters) say (of you, O Messenger): \"He has fabricated it (invented all those stories and the Qur’an containing them)?\" Say: \"If indeed I fabricate it, then upon me falls my sin, but (as you are slandering me to excuse your own willful persistence in unbelief, know that) I am free of the sins you have been committing"